Project_Description: A fullstack web app that visualizes all the frame data for the character Bridget from Guilty Gear Strive
A frontend project where I took a UI/UX design and implemented it using the React Framework. Frontend styling project only (no functionality outside main page).

A frontend weather app that uses OpenWeather API to give details on the current weather, the weather in the next few hours, and the weather in the next few days. The app also uses an autocorrect api to give cities that works.
